title: ***2b/1b at 7401 W 101st Street, Bloomington (Countryside West)
posting_body: ['Luxury 2b/1b condo in Countryside West Condominiums.', 'Close to Bush Lake, Hyland Park Reserve and more!', 'One month free!', 'Experience an Extraordinary living in this luxury 2 bedroom condo located on 101st Street West, Bloomington.', 'This newly remodeled two bedroom condo is great for all ages has everything a person looking for: big bedrooms, washer and dryer, all kitchen appliances, huge deck, heated underground parking, and storage space down the hall right next to the community room.', '2b/1b condo            1000sqf', 'Rent $1,525         Garage                Storage', 'Rental Features:', '*Living room                *Refrigerator                                    *Stove/Oven', '*Dishwasher                 *Dining room                                    *Washer/dryer in the unit', '*Fireplace                     *A/C                                                   *Basic digital cable included', '*Glass backsplash in the kitchen', '*New maintenance free deck and railing', 'Community Features:', '*Garage parking                                *Storage unit           *Secure building', '*Heated underground parking         *Outdoor pool        *Community room', 'Lease Terms:', 'We are looking for a responsible tenant who is a non-smoker, without a pet to sign a min one-year lease.', 'Long-term lease preferred.', 'Require a credit/background check.', 'Please call Olesya at', 'show contact info', '.']
